name: メイ - Rosa Pokemon
description:
A LoRA of Rosa from Pokémon Black 2 and White 2. Trained on NAI.

See samples for good prompts. Works well in most of the anime based LoRAs.

If you enjoy this LoRA, please let a review!

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
